44
00:02:06,232 --> 00:02:08,930
The judge ordered him to be sent
to the Siu Lam Psychiatric Center.

45
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:10,840
Why was he later transferred
to this hospital?

46
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,339
After serving his sentence

47
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:14,520
at Siu Lam,

48
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:16,210
