92
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,960
I want to go out.

93
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:47,080
Don't cry, Bao.

94
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,499
No one

95
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:51,290
in this world cares about us.

96
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:53,680
You need to stay strong, okay?

97
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:58,520
Come here.

98
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:00,170
I'll hug you.

99
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:02,640
I'll hug you.

100
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:07,960
According to the director,

101
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,649
Mai Zhihong suffers
from schizophrenia,

102
00:04:09,650 --> 00:04:12,200
hallucinations, hearing things,
and feeling things that aren't there.

103
00:04:12,380 --> 00:04:14,749
Bao is a hallucination

104
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,010
only Mai Zhihong can see.

105
00:04:16,590 --> 00:04:18,280
He calls him Bao

106
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,779
because when he was young,

107
00:04:19,780 --> 00:04:22,210
he was constantly bullied
by his schoolmates and cried a lot.

108
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,024
They would mock him,
calling him a crybaby.

109
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:24,909
Bao represents

110
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:26,720
Mai Zhihong's most vulnerable

111
00:04:26,860 --> 00:04:28,010
and self-conscious side.

112
