the police force.

118
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,659
If the officers find any leads,

119
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:32,770
they'll follow up on them.

120
00:05:32,860 --> 00:05:34,219
If you can't handle it,

121
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:35,520
we can help you.

122
00:05:35,544 --> 00:05:37,280
It's not like
we haven't done this before.

123
00:05:46,664 --> 00:05:48,480
If you want to avoid trouble
in the future,

124
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:50,859
