130
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,370
and expose all of us?

131
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:05,720
I can find the guy.

132
00:06:06,150 --> 00:06:07,389
But I won't get involved

133
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,690
