134
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:09,450
Why?

135
00:06:09,784 --> 00:06:11,640
Are you afraid
we'll drag you down with us?

136
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:14,010
We're all in the same boat here.

137
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,149
Nobody knows

138
00:06:15,150 --> 00:06:16,480
