183
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:27,939
♪I wish you won't throw♪

184
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:31,690
♪The burden guilt on my shoulder♪

185
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:34,579
♪My heart is still as water♪

186
00:09:34,580 --> 00:09:35,690
Officer Yao,

187
00:09:35,940 --> 00:09:38,330
