00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:32,499
The 1990 King Shun Building Fire

726
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:34,019
had claimed countless lives

727
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:34,920
and homes.

728
00:35:35,620 --> 00:35:38,240
Even the survivors
didn't have it easy.

729
00:35:38,500 --> 00:35:40,130
After all these years,

730
00:35:41,020 --> 00:35:42,840
I still have nightmares.

731
00:35:43,790 --> 00:35:46,210
I would dream about that night.

732
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:49,240
There were flames everywhere.

733
00:35:49,390 --> 00:35:50,840
The smoke was so thick.

734
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:52,840
My name is Zheng Wenxin.

735
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:54,920
I was only four

736
00:35:55,310 --> 00:35:56,610
that year.

737
00:35:57,060 --> 00:35:58,090
At that time,

738
00:35:58,190 --> 00:36:00,170
I was engulfed in flames.

739
00:36:00,910 --> 00:36:02,400
I almost lost my life.

740
00:36:04,140 --> 00:36:05,050
Also,

741
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:07,800
I'm incredibly grateful
to the charitable foundation

742
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:11,189
that has supported survivors like us

743
00:36:11,190 --> 00:36:13,610
through tough times.

744
00:36:14,060 --> 00:36:15,050
I truly hope

745
00:36:15,830 --> 00:36:16,789
such tragedies

746
00:36:16,790 --> 00:36:18,240
never happen again.

747
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:20,210
Was it an accident

748
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:22,240
or arson?

749
00:36:22,910 --> 00:36:24,320
I've been thinking about that too.

750
00:36:24,344 --> 00:36:26,328
That's why I've been reviewing
the old case files

751
00:36:26,344 --> 00:36:27,784
to see if we overlooked any clues.

752
00:36:28,060 --> 00:36:29,720
We must follow up on the lead

753
00:36:29,830 --> 00:36:30,880
on Black Guy Tian.

754
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:32,909
If it turns out

755
00:36:32,910 --> 00:36:34,570
he was behind the incident back then,

756
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:36,400
how can we let that slide

757
00:36:36,620 --> 00:36:38,010
when 39 lives had been lost?

758
00:36:38,710 --> 00:36:40,090
He must have some powerful support.

759
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:41,640
Now his right-hand man, Biao the Blind,

760
00:36:41,656 --> 00:36:43,080
has taken over all the operations.

761
00:36:43,336 --> 00:36:45,704
He's handling the same things
Black Guy Tian did back then.

762
00:36:46,420 --> 00:36:48,240
If someone really sets
the fire on purpose,

763
00:36:48,310 --> 00:36:49,419
the mastermind

764
00:36:49,420 --> 00:36:50,059
is likely tied

765
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:51,440
to those same people.

766
00:36:53,736 --> 00:36:55,240
The Anti-Triad Squad gave us a tip.

767
00:36:55,288 --> 00:36:56,760
Biao the Blind is hosting a gathering

768
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:57,779
