769
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:59,920
No details yet on who's attending
or what's the agenda.

770
00:36:59,928 --> 00:37:00,430
Jiajie.

771
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:01,140
Kaiqing.

772
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:03,064
I want both of you
to follow up on this lead.

773
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:05,080
As for the rest of you,
keep digging for more clues.

774
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:07,510
- Yes, sir.
