807
00:39:10,470 --> 00:39:11,210
This way, please.

808
00:39:12,390 --> 00:39:13,460
Who's this guy?

809
00:39:13,990 --> 00:39:14,900
I'm not sure.

810
00:39:15,200 --> 00:39:16,600
He looks like someone important.

811
00:39:27,470 --> 00:39:29,290
(Bluetooth Not Connected)

812
00:39:29,815 --> 00:39:30,770
(Bluetooth Connected)

813
00:39:46,950 --> 00:39:47,770
Stay still.

814
00:39:48,790 --> 00:39:49,650
Why?

815
00:39:51,790 --> 00:39:52,730
What is it?

816
00:39:53,200 --> 00:39:54,340
That's impressive.

817
00:39:54,390 --> 00:39:55,420
It can even record videos.

818
00:39:56,310 --> 00:39:57,420
