819
00:39:57,520 --> 00:39:58,940
It works like a dashcam.

820
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,250
You'll keep watch here.

821
00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:03,090
Let me go.

822
00:40:03,950 --> 00:40:05,208
