842
00:41:27,040 --> 00:41:28,389
Things are heating up lately.

843
00:41:28,390 --> 00:41:29,610
So don't act recklessly.

844
00:41:30,310 --> 00:41:31,989
The ICAC is reviewing files

845
00:41:31,990 --> 00:41:33,340
to investigate those tycoons.

846
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:35,559
Every newspaper is covering

847
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:37,540
the land-hoarding scandal.

848
00:41:38,470 --> 00:41:40,020
Be careful when you're out and about

849
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:44,820
and make your fortune quietly.

850
00:41:45,350 --> 00:41:46,650
Keep a low profile.

851
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:48,690
Especially you.

852
00:41:49,310 --> 00:41:50,460
Lay low.

